PN,42401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FThe family of a man from Redcar have
OL,7,Fsaid they are grateful after a coroner
OL,8,Fruled that delays to the arrival of an
OL,9,Fambulance crew possibly contributed to
OL,10,Fhis death.
OL,12,FThe coroner concluded that former
OL,13,Fsteelworker Peter Coates would not
OL,14,Fhave died when he did, had it not been
OL,15,Ffor an unexpected power cut which
OL,16,Fstopped the home oxygen supply he
OL,17,Frelied on.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FPeter Coates was 62 when he died seven
OL,7,Fyears ago and had faced a number of
OL,8,Fhealth issues in the later stages of
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FHe had developed lung cancer, though
OL,12,Fhis inquest heard he had since been in
OL,13,Fremission.
OL,15,FHis family said today the seven-year
OL,16,Fbattle to get the verdict had been
OL,17,F"pretty tough on all of us".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FMr Coates' daughter Kellie Coates
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've all had our own
OL,8,Fchallenges trying to deal with it.
OL,9,FThere's been times when we've all
OL,10,Fwanted to just give in.
OL,12,F"Now we can just start remembering the
OL,13,Fgood things about him, start thinking
OL,14,Fpositively instead of always having
OL,15,Fthis hanging over our heads."
OL,17,FMr Coates also lived with a severe
OL,18,Fform of the lung condition, COPD, and
OL,19,Frelied on an electrically-powered
OL,20,Foxygen machine in order to breathe.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FWhen a power blackout cut that oxygen
OL,7,Fsupply, just before 4am on 14 March
OL,8,F2019, Mr Coates clearly knew the
OL,9,Fdanger he was in.
OL,11,FIn a recording of the 999 call he made
OL,12,Fto the North East Ambulance Service,
OL,13,Fplayed to the coroner, he was heard to
OL,14,Fsay: "You'd better get someone quick".
OL,16,FThe inquest was told that a series of
OL,17,Fissues delayed the arrival of an
OL,18,Fambulance crew and when paramedics
OL,19,Ffound Mr Coates, he was lying dead in
OL,20,Fhis bedroom.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FFrom the time of his call, at 4:01am,
OL,7,Fit was 47 minutes before help reached
OL,8,Fhis bedside.
OL,10,FThe inquest heard that Mr Coates had
OL,11,Fmanaged to retrieve a portable oxygen
OL,12,Fcylinder during that time, and
OL,13,Fattached it to nasal cannula.
OL,15,FMs Coates told the hearing that she
OL,16,Fand her family remain "haunted" by
OL,17,Fwhat he had been through during that
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,20,FTimeline of 14 March 2019
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,F4:01am - Peter Coates calls 999,
OL,7,Fexplaining there had been a power cut
OL,8,Fand saying "you'd better get someone
OL,9,Fquick".
OL,11,F4:04am - Crew from Redcar allocated
OL,12,Fbut was unable to open the ambulance
OL,13,Fstation gates because of the power cut.
OL,15,F4:15 - Second crew from Coulby Newham
OL,16,Fallocated.
OL,18,F4:23 - Ambulance stops to refuel
OL,19,Fdespite already carrying nearly half a
OL,20,Ftank of diesel, the inquest heard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,F4:27 - Ambulance leaves the fuel
OL,7,Fstation.
OL,9,F4:38 - Ambulance arrives as Mr Coates'
OL,10,Fhome but crew struggles to find safe
OL,11,Fbox for key to let themselves into
OL,12,Fhouse.
OL,14,F4:48 - Crew enters house and finds Mr
OL,15,FCoates upstairs.
OL,17,FFor the family of Peter Coates, today
OL,18,Fmarks a significant moment in a long
OL,19,Fand painful story.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FBorn in Guisborough, Mr Coates spent
OL,7,Fmost of his life in Dormanstown near
OL,8,FRedcar, working at British Steel for
OL,9,Fforty years.
OL,11,FHe was a father to five children and
OL,12,Flater became a proud grandfather.
OL,14,FThe love felt for Mr Coates by his
OL,15,Ffamily was clear when I first met his
OL,16,Fdaughter Kellie and son Ian in the
OL,17,Fsummer of 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FAt that stage, they were grappling
OL,7,Fwith details about the circumstances
OL,8,Fof their father's death which had come
OL,9,Fto light several years after he passed
OL,10,Faway.
OL,12,FWe met at South Gare, close to the
OL,13,Fmouth of the River Tees, and a
OL,14,Ffavourite spot of Mr Coates'.
OL,16,FIt was a place where his family could
OL,17,Fcome to remember him.
OL,19,FThere, Ms Coates told me they were
OL,20,Fpressing for a full inquest into her
OL,21,Ffather's death.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,F"It's about having the truth," she
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,FStep forward three-and-a-half years,
OL,10,Fand that inquest has now concluded.
OL,12,FThe coroner ruled Mr Coates died due
OL,13,Fto complications from very severe
OL,14,FCOPD, coupled with the consequences of
OL,15,Fobesity. He found the grandfather
OL,16,Fwould not have died when he did had
OL,17,Fthe power cut not occurred.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FThe coroner also pointed to a series
OL,7,Fof improvements introduced by the
OL,8,FNorth East Ambulance Service in the
OL,9,Fseven years since Mr Coates' death.
OL,10,FThese include a new system for
OL,11,Finvestigating incidents, training on
OL,12,Fhow to manually over ride station
OL,13,Fgates and steps to explore whether
OL,14,Fambulance fuel information can be sent
OL,15,Fremotely to the organisation's control
OL,16,Fcentre.
OL,18,FMr Coates' family only became aware of
OL,19,Fthe issues surrounding the arrival of
OL,20,Fan ambulance some years later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FHis case was examined as part of a
OL,7,Freview, led by Dame Marianne Griffiths
OL,8,Fand published in 2023, into
OL,9,Fallegations of failures and cover-ups
OL,10,Fat the North East Ambulance Service.
OL,12,FDame Marianne observed that "the
OL,13,Freality was that if the ambulance crew
OL,14,Fhad arrived earlier than they did, the
OL,15,Fpatient may not have deteriorated so
OL,16,Frapidly and died".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,FIn a statement, North East Ambulance
OL,7,FService's deputy chief executive Karen
OL,8,FO'Brien said: "This is a tragic
OL,9,Fincident which we understand has
OL,10,Fdeeply affected the family and those
OL,11,Fstaff at NEAS who were involved. We
OL,12,Fare truly sorry that we were not
OL,13,Fquicker in responding to Mr Coates'
OL,14,Fcall.
OL,16,F"We have made several changes to our
OL,17,Fprocesses since this happened, which
OL,18,Fhave been considered during the
OL,19,Finquest and which were acknowledged by
OL,20,Fthe Coroner during his detailed ruling
OL,21,Fin court today.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774275077
OL,3,CAmbulance delay 'possibly' contributed
OL,4,Cto grandfather's death, coroner rules
OL,6,F"We recognise that the time it's taken
OL,7,Fto reach this conclusion has impacted
OL,8,FMr Coates' loved ones and we wish to
OL,9,Fonce again pass on our sincere
OL,10,Fcondolences to his family for their
OL,11,Fvery sad loss."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/14
